</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:352px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Forbidden_city_map_wp_1.png" class="image" title="Plan of the Forbidden City. Labels in red will be used to refer to locations throughout the article.  - - - Approximate dividing line between Inner (north) and Outer (south) Courts.      A. Meridian Gate B. Gate of Divine Might C. West Glorious Gate D. East Glorious Gate E. Corner towers F. Gate of Supreme Harmony G. Hall of Supreme Harmony   H. Hall of Military Eminence J. Hall of Literary Glory K. Southern Three Places L. Palace of Heavenly Purity M. Imperial garden N. Hall of Mental Cultivation O. Palace of Tranquil Longevity  "><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/Forbidden_city_map_wp_1.png/350px-Forbidden_city_map_wp_1.png" width="350" height="416" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
